site.title: PRiVY join our matrix #era:privy.ws
site.description: PrivyERA initiatives is a mixed bag of acquaintances. We come together under as one culture, one crew. From all around the world. We shares common goals, ideas and mindstate and freedom of data/speech. We strives to provide a open/decentralized platform to facilitates communications , files sharing and helping people to deploy their own project if it abide and fit our goals and strict politic about our users privacy and security. Privy, PrivyERA, Privy and intelsway , I.S.P , intel sway PrivyERA is a decentralized community hub idea.
